<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>kěn qiú zhǔ 迦南532</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 kěn qiú zhǔ, jié jìng wǒ, róng yào nǐ, wèi nǐ huó,
 bù yuàn zuò shēng xiù qì mǐn. zhǔ rén qì, wú zhe luò,
 bù yuàn xiàng tán huā yī xiàn, zhuǎn yǎn jiān jiù xiāo méi,
 yuàn zuò yī kē zhǎng qīng shù, duō jié guǒ, yè bù luò,
 zhè gè fú qì yào dé zhe, zhēn xǐ lè.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>532</hymn_number>
</song>